sequenceDiagram
    participant Dev as Developer
    participant GH as GitHub<br/>notebooks repo
    participant Konflux as Konflux CI
    participant Cachi2 as Cachi2 Prefetch<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant Registry as registry.redhat.io<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant Operator as rhods-operator<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS
    participant Cluster as OpenShift Cluster<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS
    participant Dashboard as RHOAI Dashboard
    participant Controller as odh-notebook-controller
    participant User as User Browser
    participant Gateway as RHOAI Gateway<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    participant KRBAC as kube-rbac-proxy<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS mTLS
    participant Workbench as Workbench Container<br/>8888/TCP HTTP

    Note over Dev, Registry: Flow 1: Image Build and Deployment Pipeline

    Dev->>GH: Push code changes<br/>HTTPS/443, SSH key / PAT
    GH->>Konflux: Trigger build pipeline
    Konflux->>Cachi2: Prefetch dependencies<br/>(RPMs, pip, Go, npm)<br/>HTTPS/443, Service account
    Cachi2-->>Konflux: Cached + hash-verified artifacts
    Note over Konflux: Hermetic container build<br/>(no network access)
    Konflux->>Registry: Push built images<br/>HTTPS/443, Registry credentials
    Operator->>Cluster: Apply ImageStream manifests<br/>HTTPS/6443, ServiceAccount token

    Note over User, Workbench: Flow 2: User Workbench Access

    User->>Dashboard: Select workbench image<br/>HTTPS/443, OAuth token
    Dashboard->>Cluster: Create Notebook CR<br/>HTTPS/6443, OAuth token
    Controller->>Registry: Pull workbench image<br/>HTTPS/443, Pull secret
    Registry-->>Controller: Container image
    Note over Controller: Create StatefulSet pod<br/>+ inject kube-rbac-proxy sidecar
    User->>Gateway: Access workbench<br/>HTTPS/443, TLS 1.2+<br/>OAuth/OIDC redirect
    Gateway->>KRBAC: Forward request<br/>HTTPS/8443, mTLS<br/>Bearer token forwarded
    KRBAC->>Workbench: Proxy to workbench<br/>HTTP/8888 (pod-internal)<br/>Pre-authorized by proxy
    Workbench-->>KRBAC: Response
    KRBAC-->>Gateway: Response
    Gateway-->>User: Workbench UI
